Package: anope
Version: 2.0.6-1
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Dominic Hargreaves <dom@earth.li>
Installed-Size: 20379
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.14), libgcc1 (>= 1:3.0), libgnutls30 (>= 3.5.6), libldap-2.4-2 (>= 2.4.7), libmariadbclient18 (>= 10.1.28), libpcre3, libsqlite3-0 (>= 3.5.9), libstdc++6 (>= 5.2), lsb-base (>= 3.2-14)
Recommends: default-mta | mail-transport-agent
Section: net
Priority: optional
Homepage: http://www.anope.org/
Description: IRC Services designed for flexibility and ease of use
 Anope offers various services to maintain your IRC network.
 .
 The following main services are included: NickServ, ChanServ, MemoServ,
 OperServ, BotServ, and HostServ.
 .
 The following IRC servers are supported:
 .
  * Bahamut 1.4.27 or later (including 1.8)
  * Charybdis 3.4 or later
  * Hybrid 8.2 or later
  * InspIRCd 1.2 or 2.0
  * ngIRCd 19.2 or later
  * Plexus 3 or later
  * Ratbox 2.0.6 or later
  * UnrealIRCd 3.2 or later
